I'll get into hot water for saying this, but I suppose oil workers, like all migrant workers, move around the world a lot to other oil ports and rigs, and when on shore have contact with people in the sex trade, posing a risk of spreading EVD. And the same applies to delegates who attend international conferences. - Mod.JW

